CI/CD
to generate report in cucumber
Steps:
1. add plugins in pom.xml-help us in reporting mechanism
    maven SureFire

2.from the runner class we state the type of report on plugins
tag plugin={"pretty","html:target/cucumber.html","json:target/cucumber.json"}

What is the purpose of having a failedRunner?
we want to rerun test to make sure the cause of failure.

What is Maven life cycle?
it is the phases in maven build system.
the test execute the test cases indicated in the
runner class